body_html: @colmantse It looks like something is failing in the RE2 build, apparently in test code. Since we don't need that code, I've created PR #14696 to disable it. Could you please try patching it in (or making the one-line change to tensorflow/contrib/cmake/external/re2.cmake) and let us know if that fixes things?
